DERIVATIVE WORK

ESPHome Configuration Modifications
https://github.com/[your-username]/[your-repo]

This work is a derivative of the original Sensorbox V2 project by Thomas
Sanladerer, modified to:

  - Migrate the display driver from the deprecated ili9xxx platform to
    the current mipi_spi platform
  - Refactor the display lambda for improved code efficiency
  - Add an LVGL-based display implementation using arc gauge widgets
  - Add QNH sea-level pressure correction for the BMP280 sensor
  - Various configuration improvements and updates for ESPHome 2026.x

This derivative work is released under the same Creative Commons Attribution
4.0 International License as the original.

